text: Richard "Dickie" Rock (10October 19366December 2024) was an Irish singer- songwriter. He was well known as a member of The Miami Showband in the 1960s. He represented Ireland as a solo singer in the Eurovision Song Contest 1966. He retired in 2021. Rock died at a hospital in Dublin, Ireland on 6December 2024, at the age of 88. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:2024 deaths Category:Irish singer-songwriters Category:Singers from Dublin Category:Writers from Dublin Category:Eurovision Song Contest entrants
